Description: This thing is pretty much brand new. Bought on a whim, but I haven't caught on with the tenor style or played it much at all. Comes with a gig bag. Neat little guitar. I believe this model is no longer in production. Check my feedback rating and bid with confidence. No known issues. Plays well. Good action, straight neck. I pack well and ship fast. Specs: 4 string electric guitar is tuned in 5ths instead of 4ths, and boasts a basswood body with a natural finish, mini-humbucker and single coil pickup configuration with 2 volumes and 1 tone control, a 23" scale bolt-on maple neck with rosewood fingerboard, adjustable T-style bridge, and chrome sealed tuners. Includes: Gig Bag.
